       <h1>Tips For Becoming a Translator</h1> 
       <h3> <span class="warn_text">Repost</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; <span> <em>Jan 02, 2014</em> <b>By Trey Archer , eChinacities.com</b></span> <span> <a href="#page_cmt"><font style="color:red">Comments&nbsp;(3)</font></a> &nbsp; &nbsp; <a href="#cmt_box">Add your comment</a> <a style="color:red" href="/index/unsubscribe?page=2" class="newslet_bg">Newsletter</a> </span> </h3> 
       <style type="text/css">
			.article_left .articleShare li span{ float:none; padding-left:0;}
			#at-cv-lightbox{ display:none;}
			</style> 
       <div class="article_left" style=" border:none"> 
        <!-- JiaThis Button BEGIN --> 
        <div class="jiathis_style"> 
         <ul class="addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style addthis_16x16_style articleShare" style="padding-bottom:0"> 
